nBalancing the criteria\u2014reliability, decision\u2011making, calm performance under pressure, and especially crew teamwork for long\u2011distance operations\u2014**Candidate\u202fC** currently appears to best satisfy the most critical requirements.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
